04:46.709 --> 04:53.980
time, They organized this National Extension 
Center for Advanced Study at University of

04:55.107 --> 05:07.283
Wisconsin, financed by Kellogg. And they gave 
fellowships, which means you didn't have to work.

05:13.691 --> 05:17.196
