if you could qualify. Well, I had a choice of going

05:17.636 --> 05:19.579
to There was another program that several 
administrators participated in was the public

05:20.335 --> 05:25.403
administration program at Harvard. But you'd get 
a doctorate of public administration, which,

05:26.044 --> 05:39.003
although it would have been nice to go to Harvard 
and have that in your record, I thought a PhD was

05:26.044 --> 05:39.003
probably better from anywhere else. And 
Wisconsin was fairly respectable as far as the

05:39.103 --> 05:44.551
graduate school is concerned. Anyway, Kellogg 
provided a grant for five years of getting Oh, a

05:50.980 --> 05:59.209
couple of dozen or so young people or mid-career 
people identified that might have other

05:50.980 --> 05:59.209
administrative potential. And it was a 
competitive thing. You applied, and if you got it,

06:01.872 --> 06:08.759
