17:01.103 --> 17:06.591
appreciation don't realize what they have with 
the extension service. And I think Mr. Rudder

17:07.192 --> 17:18.309
understood that, and I think he used the extension 
service for... Can you think of any examples where

17:07.192 --> 17:18.309
he demonstrated how well he could relate to 
agricultural people? Mr. Rudder? Yeah, places

17:19.451 --> 17:23.437
where he used to... Well, he was always at home in 
agricultural circles. I mean, he had no

17:23.457 --> 17:26.942
problem... Well, I guess he was at home in all kinds 
